# Navigation

- NavigationStack + NavigationPath; .navigationDestination(for:) for type-safe routing
- TabView as root; per-tab NavigationStack
- Sheets: .sheet, .fullScreenCover
- macOS: NavigationSplitView for sidebar on larger screens
- Deep links: onOpenURL
